item.title: Piano Has No Tears Left to Cry - sideswipeBL
item.dc:creator: anon86704580
item.description:
I like those chords. Kinda sharp piano at the start. Maybe lowpass a bit. Ariana Grande is cool and all, but this lit. 1:20 is a cool breakdown! Yea all together awesome song! A little repetitive at times. Don’t know if that’s what you’re aiming for though, or if that’s how the sing goes.

Uniqueness: 7/10
Predictability: 6/10
Complexity: 8/10
Use of Instruments/Automation/Samples: 7/10
Feeling: 8/10

Overall: 36/50
